Date: Sun, 01 Jul 2007 12:31:23 -0400
From: bo yang <>
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] scsi: megaraid_sas -- add hibernation support
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2007/7/3/365

The megaraid_sas driver doesn't support the hibernation, the
suspend/resume routine implemented to support the hibernation.
Signed-off-by: Bo Yang <bo.yang@lsi.com>
---
